snippet.title: Solo - what does love mean to developers?
snippet.description:
http://fig.co/solo

Solo is a personal experience for those who enjoy puzzle and narratively creative indie games. Solo is an exploration game in which a sailor is traveling through a vast archipelago, solving puzzles, and wondering about love.

Devs in order of appearance:

- George Batchelor
- Toby Fox
- Rosa Carbo-Mascarell
- Luis Díaz Peralta
- Alayna M Cole
- Mirella Díez
- Jordi de Paco, Marina and Pablo from Deconstructeam

@TeamGotham_
